        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;Hi {!$Record.The_Ultimate_Parent_Account__r.Owner.FirstName},&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;{!$User.FirstName} {!$User.LastName} just added &lt;a href=&quot;{!forT_LinkAccount}&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;{!$Record.Name}&lt;/a&gt; to the &lt;a href=&quot;{!forT_LinkUltimateParent}&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;{!$Record.The_Ultimate_Parent_Account__r.Name} &lt;/a&gt;hierarchy. If this is correct, please disregard this email. If this is inaccurate, or might cause any kind of data quality issues such as duplicates or jobs that later need to be moved, please act ASAP to work with {!$User.FirstName} and/or the Sales Ops team to update the information.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thank you!&lt;/p&gt;</text>
    </textTemplates>
